# Main/Util.elm — EARLY

Pure leaf utilities used across `Main.*` modules. Zero
domain dependencies; safe for any `Main.*` module to import
without import-cycle risk.

## Status

- **Label:** EARLY. Created 2026-04-28 during elm_cleanup
  stage 3 dispatch 4 (MAIN_UTIL cluster) to consolidate
  helpers that had been duplicated across `Main.State` and
  `Main.View`.

## Exports

- `listAt : Int -> List a -> Maybe a` — safe positional
  index. Previously duplicated in `Main.State` and
  `Main.View`; identical copies also live in `Game.Game`
  and `Game.GestureArbitration` (out of scope of the
  current cleanup; future Game/-pass can import from here
  or factor a Game-side twin).
- `pluralize : Int -> String -> String` — render a
  count + noun with English-style pluralization. Used by
  `popupFromOutcome` in `Main.View`.

## Pointers

- Callers today: `Main.State` (listAt only),
  `Main.View` (both).
- elm_cleanup stage 1 inventory:
  `~/showell_repos/claude-steve/elm_cleanup/outputs/01-smells.md`
  smells A1 + A3.
